import React, { useState } from 'react' const LifeExpectancyComponent = props => { const { onSubmitHandler, initialDate, initialGender } = props const [date, setDate] = useState(initialDate) const [gender, setGender] = useState(initialGender) return (
{ onSubmitHandler(e, { date, gender }) }} >
{ setDate(e.target.value) }} value={date} />
) } export default LifeExpectancyComponent
